* Synthetic single-supply opamp subcircuit for the dual_subckt QA fixture.
*
* This is NOT a real device model.  It exists only so that two schematic
* symbols can share one .subckt library model, exercising the SPICE export
* path that must keep both references on the library name (see
* NetlistExporterSpice/SharedSubcktModelKeepsItsName).  The body is a trivial
* ideal VCVS; only the .SUBCKT name and pin list matter to the test.

.SUBCKT OPA192 +IN -IN V+ V- Vout
Eout Vout 0 +IN -IN 1e6
.ENDS OPA192
